Package mystars.forms

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IUserInterface
    This interface manages the respective forms for the operation of MySTARS.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AccessPeriodResponse
    This class holds the information for the MySTARS access period starting and ending date and time.
    AdminMenuResponse
    This class manages the form for administrators with relevant options.
    CourseManagementResponse
    This class manages the form for the management of courses with the relevant options.
    CreateCourseResponse
    This class manages the form for the creation of courses.
    CreateIndexResponse
    This class manages the form for the creation of course indexes.
    CreateLessonResponse
    This class manages the form for the creation of course index lessons.
    CreateStudentResponse
    This class manages the form for the creation of students.
    IndexManagementResponse
    This class manages the the form for the management of course indexes with the relevant options.
    IndexSwopResponse
    This class manages the form for students to swap their index with another student.
    LoginResponse
    This class manages the form for the user's login.
    StudentMenuResponse
    This class manages the form for students with the relevant options.
    TextResponse
    This class manages the text in the form being displayed in the user interface.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AdminMenuResponse.Selected
    Enum containing the options available to administrators.
    CourseManagementResponse.Selected
    Enum containing the options for managing courses.
    IndexManagementResponse.Selected
    Enum containing the options for managing course indexes.
    StudentMenuResponse.Selected
    Enum containing the options for students to manage their courses.
